Troubleshooting
Issue: Jinja2 template not found

Verify template files are in templates/ directory
Check file extensions are .j2
Ensure FileSystemLoader points to correct directory
Issue: YAML parsing errors

Validate YAML syntax using: python3 -c "import yaml; yaml.safe_load(open('data/dev_config.yaml'))"
Check indentation (use spaces, not tabs)
Ensure colons have space after them
Issue: Validation fails unexpectedly

Print the loaded config to debug: print(yaml.safe_load(open('configs/app_config.yaml')))
Verify schema path is correct
Check that generated YAML is valid
Issue: Generated config has extra whitespace

Ensure Jinja2 Environment uses trim_blocks=True and lstrip_blocks=True
Use {%- and -%} in templates to strip whitespace
